body:
#### PR description:

The aim of this PR is to update the Tracker Alignment PV Validation and PV Resolution per run submission tools.
The list of features introduced in this PR are:
  * added the executable script: `submitPVValidationJobs.py`;
  * added possibility of configuring refitter sequence and CPE type from submission;
  * updated the example ini files with the lauching script, now in the path;
  * updated unit test to run job submitters;
  * included all modification to be compliant with both Py2 and Py3;

#### PR validation:

Relies on the existing (and augmented) unit tests, both in the regular build  `CMSSW_11_2_X_2020-10-01-2300` and in the Py3 build  `CMSSW_11_2_PY3_X_2020-10-04-2300`.

#### if this PR is a backport please specify the original PR and why you need to backport that PR:

This is not a backport, and no backport is immediately needed.
